## Theming — override in `src/styles/global.css`

Map HeroUI's internal tokens to the app's `@theme` design tokens.
Add this block **after** `@import '@heroui/styles'`:

```css
:root {
  /* Map HeroUI primary → app brand (gold) */
  --heroui-primary:      theme(colors.brand);      /* = var(--color-brand) */
  --heroui-primary-200:  theme(colors.brand-light);
  --heroui-primary-700:  theme(colors.brand-dim);

  /* Backgrounds */
  --heroui-background:   theme(colors.page);       /* = var(--color-page) */
  --heroui-content1:     theme(colors.surface);
  --heroui-content2:     theme(colors.elevated);

  /* Divider */
  --heroui-divider:      rgb(255 255 255 / 0.06);  /* = border-white/6 */
}
```

