## Full Component Reference

### Layout & Structure
| Component | Import | When to use |
|-----------|--------|-------------|
| `Card, CardHeader, CardBody, CardFooter` | `@heroui/react/card` | Standard cards (use `GlassCard` for custom dark glass effect) |
| `Divider` | `@heroui/react/divider` | Section separators |
| `Spacer` | `@heroui/react/spacer` | Vertical/horizontal whitespace |
| `ScrollShadow` | `@heroui/react/scroll-shadow` | Scrollable container with fade shadow |
| `Navbar, NavbarBrand, NavbarContent, NavbarItem, NavbarMenuToggle, NavbarMenu, NavbarMenuItem` | `@heroui/react/navbar` | Top navigation bar (replaces custom `Navbar.tsx`) |

### Inputs & Forms
| Component | Import | When to use |
|-----------|--------|-------------|
| `Button, ButtonGroup` | `@heroui/react/button` | Every button in the app |
| `Input` | `@heroui/react/input` | Single-line text input |
| `Textarea` | `@heroui/react/textarea` | Multi-line text input |
| `NumberInput` | `@heroui/react/number-input` | Numeric input (upscale factor) |
| `InputOtp` | `@heroui/react/input-otp` | OTP / verification codes |
| `Select, SelectItem, SelectSection` | `@heroui/react/select` | Dropdown selection (output format, scale factor) |
| `Checkbox, CheckboxGroup` | `@heroui/react/checkbox` | Single or grouped checkboxes |
| `RadioGroup, Radio` | `@heroui/react/radio` | Single-choice selection |
| `Switch` | `@heroui/react/switch` | On/off toggle |
| `Slider` | `@heroui/react/slider` | Range control (enhancement level, quality) |
| `Form` | `@heroui/react/form` | Form wrapper with validation support |
| `Autocomplete, AutocompleteItem` | `@heroui/react/autocomplete` | Input with suggestions |

### Dates & Times
| Component | Import | When to use |
|-----------|--------|-------------|
| `DateInput` | `@heroui/react/date-input` | Typed date entry |
| `DatePicker` | `@heroui/react/date-picker` | Date selection with popup |
| `DateRangePicker` | `@heroui/react/date-range-picker` | Date range selection |
| `TimeInput` | `@heroui/react/time-input` | Time entry |
| `Calendar` | `@heroui/react/calendar` | Full calendar view |
| `RangeCalendar` | `@heroui/react/range-calendar` | Calendar with range selection |

### Feedback & Status
| Component | Import | When to use |
|-----------|--------|-------------|
| `Spinner` | `@heroui/react/spinner` | Loading indicator |
| `Progress` | `@heroui/react/progress` | Linear progress bar |
| `CircularProgress` | `@heroui/react/circular-progress` | Circular progress ring |
| `Skeleton` | `@heroui/react/skeleton` | Content placeholder while loading |
| `Alert` | `@heroui/react/alert` | Inline status message (success/error/warning) |
| `Toast` | `@heroui/react/toast` | Auto-dismissing notification popup |
| `Chip` | `@heroui/react/chip` | Status label, tag, badge |
