### Overlays & Popups
| Component | Import | When to use |
|-----------|--------|-------------|
| `Modal, ModalContent, ModalHeader, ModalBody, ModalFooter, useDisclosure` | `@heroui/react/modal` | Dialog / popup |
| `Drawer` | `@heroui/react/drawer` | Side panel that slides in |
| `Popover, PopoverTrigger, PopoverContent` | `@heroui/react/popover` | Small popup anchored to an element |
| `Tooltip` | `@heroui/react/tooltip` | Hover hint |
